'''第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Depression Two-E}}）是2006年6月初形成的一场持续时间较为短暂的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，在墨西哥西南部产生暴雨，是[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]形成的第二个热带低气压，也是这年6月东北[[太平洋|太平洋]]仅有的热带气旋。系统源于6月3日的一股[[东风波|东风波]]，起初向东北方向移动，对墨西哥[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]和[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]构成威胁，而且有达到热带风暴强度的可能。但是，气旋强度一直没有超过热带低气压标准，并因[[风切变|风切变]]以及同陆地间的相互影响而减弱，最终在距墨西哥海岸线不远处完全消散。系统在[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]产生486毫米雨量，引发[[泥石流|泥石流]]和洪灾。共有42幢房屋被淹，72人被迫离开家园，但没有出现人员丧生的报道。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Two-E 2006 track.png}}
第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压源自2006年5月下旬墨西哥南面近海的一股[[东风波|东风波]]。东风波关联有[[对流|对流区]]，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]认为外界环境有利于热带气旋发展<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2006-05-31 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]]}}</ref>。系统得到[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]强化并向北飘移，其东侧和西侧有[[反气旋|反气旋]]存在<ref>{{cite report | author = Martin Nelson | date = 2006-06-01 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | date = 2006-06-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。6月1日，对流变得更加集中<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2006-06-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，到次日清晨已发展成[[低气压|低气压区]]，并开始稳步向西北方向移动<ref name="twd62">{{cite report | author = Hugh Cobb | date = 2006-06-02 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。

系统北面的上层反气旋令外界环境有利于热带天气系统发展，对流逐渐组织成[[雨带|带状特征]]<ref name="twd62" />。系统还发展出良好的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Hugh Cobb | date = 2006-06-02 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，不过表面环流起初相对热带气旋而论还过于拉长<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie Berg | date = 2006-06-02 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion (3) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。6月3日清晨，附近的反气旋向东北方向移动，令系统上空的[[风切变|风切变]]增多，组织结构受到影响<ref>{{cite report | author = Hugh Cobb | date = 2006-06-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。不过，环流中心上空的对流有所增长<ref>{{cite report | author = RRG | date = 2006-06-03 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，气旋发展出足够有组织的对流和闭合表面环流，促使美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月3日下午15点将位于[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]][[锡瓦塔内霍|锡瓦塔内霍]]西南方向约240公里洋面的系统归类为第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2006-06-03 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115928/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。

成为热带气旋后，低气压因与陆地相互作用，还受到风切变的不利影响导致无法显著增强<ref name="disc1" />。系统稳步向东北方向移动，其中心因距海岸线较近而难以确定方位。不过，气旋的整体结构在短时间内呈现改善迹象，气象部门预计低气压会达到热带风暴强度。<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2006-06-03 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115929/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.002.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>6月4日清晨，对流已大幅减弱，环流中心部分暴露出来<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Mainelli | author2 = Beven | date = 2006-06-04 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115930/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。持续存在的风切变将大部分关联雷暴活动带到墨西哥西南沿海地区，但低气压的中心仍然位于海上<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | date = 2006-06-04 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Four | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115944/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.004.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。6月4日下午，系统从阿卡普尔科以南近海掠过，在此期间环流加速同深层对流分离<ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | date = 2006-06-04 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115945/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.006.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.discus.006.shtml? }}</ref>。6月5日凌晨，系统的环流已经消散<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Avila, Lixion A./National Hurricane Center | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Depression Two-E | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2006-07-05 | accessdate = 2014-08-28 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP022006_Two-E.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521105553/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP022006_Two-E.pdf | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-05-21 }}</ref>，其残留随后进入陆地上空<ref>{{cite report | author = Wally Barnes | date = 2006-06-05 | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_Depression_Two-E_2006.JPG|right]]
由于气象机构不能确定热带低气压是否会达到热带风暴标准<ref name="tcr" />，[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]政府向[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]蓬塔圣特尔莫（{{lang|en|Punta San Telmo}}）到格雷罗州阿卡普尔科之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2006-06-03 | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Public Advisory Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002115923/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.public.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep02/ep022006.public.002.shtml? }}</ref>。[[墨西哥国家气象局|墨西哥国家气象局]]向[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]、[[科利马州|科利马州]]、米却肯州、格雷罗州和[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]发布暴雨公告，还指出风暴有可能引发洪灾和[[泥石流|泥石流]]<ref name="smn">{{cite web | author = Alberto Hernández Unzón and Cirilo Bravo Lujano | year = 2006 | title = Resumen de la Depresión Tropical 2E del Océano Pacifico | publisher = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional (Mexico) | accessdate = 2008-11-29 | url = http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2006/pacifico/dt2/dt2e.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2007-06-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070625122540/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2006/pacifico/dt2/dt2e.pdf | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。政府官员在相应地区共计开设了21个避难所<ref name="65g">{{cite report | author = General Director of Social Communication | date = 2006-06-05 | title = Daily Information Summary}}</ref>。

热带低气压在墨西哥西南海岸沿线产生暴雨，阿卡普尔科的48小时雨量达486毫米。格雷罗雷和瓦哈卡州大部分地区的降雨量在50毫米以上<ref name="smn" />，引起山洪爆发和多起泥石流<ref name="tcr" />。气旋导致约40套房屋部分被淹，共有72人被迫离开家园<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | work = El Universal | date = 2006-06-05 | title = Amenaza depresión tropical pasar a ciclón | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | archivedate = 2015-06-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150604132605/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/61457.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/61457.html }}</ref>。洪水将阿卡普尔科街头巷尾的垃圾冲到海滩上，格雷罗州其他地区还有多条高速公路因洪水和泥石流被迫封闭<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | work = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | title = Tropical depression sparks minor flooding in Mexican Pacific resort of Acapulco | date = 2006-06-04}}</ref>，导致数十辆车被困，还有一幢监狱的围墙因降雨倒塌<ref name="65g" />。降雨导致阿卡普尔科部分树木倒塌，多条输电线缆中断，导致停电之余，还有变压器爆炸引发的火灾<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | work = El Universal | date = 2006-06-04 | title = Depresión tropical se convierte en ciclón en Guerrero | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102201201/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/353311.html | accessdate = 2015-11-20 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/353311.html | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，没有报道表明气旋有引起任何人员伤亡<ref name="tcr" />。

